    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >​<strong>《藏物》（Macabre Zealot）</strong>是一款由【灯花社ZOO】制作组独立开发的百合悬疑AVG。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的大部分，包括剧本文案，脚本程序，美工UI由制作人：@安呗沿Burns 完成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >背景制作：@绝柴薪（b站、微博）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是我们的第一款游戏，我们希望能通过《藏物》为玩家们带来一个由爱与希望构成的故事，从她们的感情中窥见美好。如果能将这份心意传达给您就再好不过了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们欢迎支持《藏物》的玩家加入讨论群：834613051，游戏相关资讯也会第一时间在群内公开，期待您的到来！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时我们开设了各平台账号：@灯花社（微博、b站、小红书同名）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏后续资讯及衍生作品仅在以上平台公开</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注：了解下方游戏内容，可提高您的游戏体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【游戏相关】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全中文配音，共九名角色、两个结局，附加一个作案人视角。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093900/extras/61dba715f17150aae49ddf4caf402cd3.poster.avif?t=1732119808\" width=400 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093900/extras/61dba715f17150aae49ddf4caf402cd3.webm?t=1732119808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093900/extras/61dba715f17150aae49ddf4caf402cd3.mp4?t=1732119808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内含多选项可选择，选项分为“普通选项”和“结局选项”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093900/extras/53cc8c1300a94ad334ffa6b1f7565e00.poster.avif?t=1732119808\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093900/extras/53cc8c1300a94ad334ffa6b1f7565e00.webm?t=1732119808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>“普通选项”为白色字体，影响玩家收到的故事线索，但不影响结局。可自行回档了解全部选项内容，完整体验游戏剧情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093900/extras/70816fbbda010cd653edea224871f93c.poster.avif?t=1732119808\" width=400 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093900/extras/70816fbbda010cd653edea224871f93c.webm?t=1732119808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093900/extras/70816fbbda010cd653edea224871f93c.mp4?t=1732119808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>“结局选项”为红色字体，影响结局走向，建议回档以体验不同结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093900/extras/d3dd90b4b9b14d7a8fdeb96b5fa453ee.webp?t=1732119808\" width=239 height=47 /></span>同时游戏内设有“返回文本”选项，为蓝色字体，点击可返回上一选项分支处，供您选择拥有更多线索量的“普通选项”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093900/extras/f14a6297133c0d0be58e87a23b9cf265.avif?t=1732119808\" width=424 height=190 /></span>游戏中的剧情环节没有恐怖元素，方便全年龄玩家游玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而调查环节则涉及血腥露骨、真实尸体描写，可能引发生理不适，我们将在进入调查环节前询问玩家是否跳过调查（跳过后会将关键细节总结罗列，无需担心），请自行考量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若善用回档功能仔细游玩，一周目便可体验全部剧情与全CG收集。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结局、CG均解锁后，游戏将开启作案人视角，进行剧情补完。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注：选项里可能还含有分支，寻找遗漏CG或剧情时请自行甄别</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【游戏角色】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093900/extras/e61bd8a63b6486a397f7d5ecab57a03a.avif?t=1732119808\" width=600 height=20